part ii  item 7   worldwide macroeconomic factors have a strong
correlation to business and consumer demand for our software, services, games and internet service offerings. we expect a broad continuation in the economic conditions and demand in fiscal year 2007 as compared to fiscal year 2006.  as open source software development and distribution evolves, we continue to seek to differentiate our products from competing products that are based on open
source software. we believe that microsofts share of server unit operating systems increased in fiscal year 2006.  summary of results for fiscal years 2006,
