part ii  item 8   allowance for doubtful accounts  the allowance for doubtful accounts reflects our best estimate of probable losses inherent in the accounts receivable balance. we determine the allowance based on known troubled
accounts, historical experience, and other currently available evidence. activity in the allowance for doubtful accounts was as follows:
